          name: "MAI LIAN SCARLETT",
          title: "Former Senior Director, Agile Transformation Office, Lumen",
          quote: "We've been able to increase throughput by 200%, which means we're delivering capabilities faster and increasing customer satisfaction.",
          caseStudy: "Read Lumen's case study →",
